from: Description Your basic pieces should be anything but. Our Danny tee is made from 100% organic cotton, soft against your skin and highly breathable. The regular fit and short sleeves make it the perfect accompaniment for any outfit; wear with jeans or chinos or layer a jumper on top when there’s a chill in the air. Look closer and you’ll notice those classic Farah details you’ve come to expect, including a set in ribbed collar and twin needle finishes to the cuffs and hem. And, of course, the embroidered golf F branding on the chest.
